channel.title: Elitestx! Just look! You wont regret it!
channel.description:
Hey everyone my name is Sam and I am currently working on a website called www.elitestx.com which would be serving as a MMORPG based website currently and the reason I have made this post here is to attract some people's attention, specifically people who are interested in these websites for more than just help. What I mean is I am looking to recruit more staff, we have about 3 members working on this project and we look forward to expanding this business and possibally getting something out of it too.
No it's not a key logged website.. No I wont ask you for your game account info... Nope I'm not going to ask for your bank info or even your phone number...
Yeah please don't contact us and waste our time if you are not serious about looking to get in some kind of MMORPG business, we could possiblly have forums about you providing your services to earn money like you do on here too buy we are focusing on a staff rightnow if you are interested PLEASE go to www.elitestx.com/forums and you will be contacted soon!
Thank you for your time!
